cwiczenie 14
wstaw must, mustn't, needn't
Boss: Have you typed those letters yet?
Secretary: No, I haven't finished. 1) [...] I type them all this morning?
B: Yes, you 2) [...], I'm afraid.
S: Very well, Sir. 3) [...] I also photocopy them?
B: No, you 4) [...] Eric can do that. Just ask him.
S: OK, I'll do that. Oh, Sir. You've got an appointment with Mr Lee at 6 o'clock. It's almost 5.30. You 5) [...] be late.
B: Oh, dear! I forgot. I'll go now
S: Do you want me to call your wife and tell her that you'll be late?
B: No, you 6) [...] do that. I'll call her.
1 must
2 must 4 needn't 6 needn't
3 Must 5 mustn't

cwiczenie 15
